      %section.page-content

        %h2 Stop writing Wordpress themes like it's 1998.

        %p.bigger
          Wordless is an opinionated Wordpress plugin that dramatically speeds up and enhances
          your custom theme creation.

        %h3 Alright, what does it offer?
        :markdown
          * A structured and clean theme organization
          * [Haml](http://haml-lang.com/) views
          * [Sass](http://sass-lang.com/) & [Compass](http://compass-style.org) stylesheets
          * [Coffeescript](http://jashkenas.github.com/coffee-script/) logic
          * 40+ Rails-like [helper methods](https://github.com/welaika/wordless/tree/master/wordless/helpers)
          * Support to view layouts and partials
          * It is released under the MIT, a nice permissive license

